<font face="Impress BT" size="55">I know toys aren't that fast.</font>

56
00:03:41,300 --> 00:03:44,840
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">I'm a rupture man who ate the Pamu Pamu Fruit.</font>

57
00:03:47,770 --> 00:03:51,580
