00:04:12,330 --> 00:04:13,800
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">fulfill my mission!</font>

64
00:04:17,600 --> 00:04:19,070
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Rebecca!</font>

65
00:04:19,770 --> 00:04:22,510
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Rupture and die!</font>

