<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Soldier, where are Franky and the others?</font>

69
00:04:38,460 --> 00:04:39,890
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">You're...</font>

70
00:04:39,890 --> 00:04:41,990
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">What, they're not with you?</font>

71
00:04:41,990 --> 00:04:44,060
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Straw Hat, we don't have time to chat!</font>

72
00:04:44,730 --> 00:04:46,300
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Straw Hat Luffy?</font>

73
00:04:47,030 --> 00:04:48,300
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Violet?!</font>

74
00:04:48,900 --> 00:04:50,880
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">How dare you...</font>

75
00:04:51,870 --> 00:04:55,510
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">How dare you betray the young master!</font>

76
00:04:55,510 --> 00:04:56,940
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Bring it on!</font>

77
00:04:56,940 --> 00:04:58,240
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">No, run!</font>

78
00:04:58,240 --> 00:04:59,010
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">What?</font>

79
00:04:59,010 --> 00:05:03,050
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">There's no time. Besides, he's exceedingly dangerous.</font>

80
00:05:03,050 --> 00:05:06,350
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">We have to hurry to the Suit Chamber on the second floor!</font>

81
00:05:06,350 --> 00:05:08,690
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Viola-sama, why are you here?</font>

82
00:05:09,290 --> 00:05:10,390
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">You know me?</font>

83
00:05:10,390 --> 00:05:13,760
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Yes, though you don't remember me.</font>

84
00:05:13,760 --> 00:05:17,830
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">I've been watching you with my Clairvoyance the whole time.</font>

85
00:05:17,830 --> 00:05:19,930
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Both you and Rebecca.</font>

86
00:05:20,600 --> 00:05:23,070
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">It must have been hard for you. Thank you.</font>

87
00:05:25,040 --> 00:05:26,410
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Violet!</font>

88
00:05:26,970 --> 00:05:30,040
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">You, traitorous woman...</font>

89
00:05:32,880 --> 00:05:34,180
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">must die! </font>

90
00:05:34,180 --> 00:05:35,850
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">I haven't betrayed anyone!</font>

91
00:05:35,850 --> 00:05:41,250
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">These past ten years, I've never once been on your side!</font>

92
00:05:41,250 --> 00:05:44,020
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Still, you've disgraced the young master!</font>

93
00:05:45,020 --> 00:05:46,490
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Helmet Puncture!</font>

94
00:05:53,270 --> 00:05:54,800
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Viola-sama!</font>

95
00:05:54,800 --> 00:05:55,500
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Oh no!</font>

96
