<font face="Impress BT" size="55">They call Doflamingo "young master"!</font>

110
00:06:37,240 --> 00:06:39,080
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">I am the young master.</font>

111
00:06:39,080 --> 00:06:41,710
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">There are intruders in the palace.</font>

112
00:06:41,710 --> 00:06:44,420
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Please wait upstairs until we dispose of them.</font>

113
